    <h1>Spam Update</h1>
    <p class="description">A Google algorithm enforcement action that penalises sites violating spam policies — from link schemes and cloaking to thin auto-generated content. Powered by <strong>SpamBrain AI</strong>, these updates roll out several times a year and cause <strong>rapid, significant ranking drops</strong> for offending sites.</p>
